Capital Markets

Company Overview of White Mountains Advisors, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
White Mountains Advisors, LLC is an asset management arm of White Mountains Insurance Group Ltd. with approximately $33.15 billion in assets under management. The firm primarily provides its services to corporations. It also manages accounts for pension and profit sharing plans. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. The firm was formerly known as OneBeacon Asset Management, Inc. White Mountains Advisors was founded in 2003 and is based in Guilford, Connecticut with an additional office in New York City.


200 Hubbard RoadGuilford, CT 06437United StatesFounded in 2003



Phone: 203-458-5800

Fax: 203-458-0754








